<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-HK">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    {# 完美補齊 SEO 標題與描述 #}
    <title>{{ title }}{% if page.url != '/' %} - DeepSeek中文網頁版指南{% endif %}</title>
    <meta name="description" content="{{ description or '提供權威的 DeepSeek 網頁版登入、API 跨界應用、自媒體提效、本地部署及跨境通訊智能優化指南。' }}">
    <meta name="keywords" content="DeepSeek網頁版, DeepSeek登入, DeepSeek香港, AI自媒體提效, DeepSeek教程">
    
    <style>
        :root { --ds-blue: #0052cc; --ds-dark: #0f172a; --bg-light: #f8fafc; --accent: #2563eb; }
        body { font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, "Helvetica Neue", Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.8; color: #334155; background: var(--bg-light); margin: 0; padding: 0; }
        a { color: var(--accent); text-decoration: none; }
        a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }
        
        /* 導航頭部：規避 h1 衝突，統一採用 div */
        .header { background: var(--ds-dark); color: white; padding: 30px 20px; text-align: center; }
        .header .logo-container { font-size: 28px; font-weight: bold; margin: 0; }
        .header .logo-container a { color: white; }
        .header p { margin: 5px 0 0 0; color: #94a3b8; font-size: 14px; }
        
        .main-nav { background: #fff; border-bottom: 1px solid #e2e8f0; text-align: center; padding: 10px; }
        .main-nav a { margin: 0 15px; font-weight: bold; color: #475569; }
        
        .wrapper { max-width: 1200px; margin: 40px auto; padding: 0 20px; display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 320px; gap: 30px; }
        @media (max-width: 960px) { .wrapper { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }
        
        .content-area { background: #fff; padding: 40px; border-radius: 12px; box-shadow: 0 4px 6px -1px rgba(0,0,0,0.05); }
        .sidebar { background: #fff; padding: 25px; border-radius: 12px; box-shadow: 0 4px 6px -1px rgba(0,0,0,0.05); height: fit-content; }
        
        /* 側邊欄最新文章鏈接 */
        .sidebar h3 { font-size: 18px; color: var(--ds-dark); border-left: 4px solid var(--ds-blue); padding-left: 10px; margin-top: 0; }
        .sidebar-list { list-style: none; padding: 0; margin: 0; }
        .sidebar-list li { padding: 10px 0; border-bottom: 1px dashed #e2e8f0; font-size: 15px; }
        
        /* 站群矩陣矩陣友情鏈接樣式 */
        .footer { background: var(--ds-dark); color: #94a3b8; padding: 40px 20px; text-align: center; margin-top: 60px; font-size: 14px; }
        .friend-links { max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto 20px auto; padding-bottom: 20px; border-bottom: 1px solid #334155; }
        .friend-links strong { color: #f1f5f9; display: block; margin-bottom: 10px; }
        .friend-links a { color: #cbd5e1; margin: 0 12px; display: inline-block; }
        .friend-links a:hover { color: white; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <header class="header">
        {# 頂部標識：純外殼容器，杜絕在內容頁和列表頁與 h1 搶權重 #}
        <div class="logo-container">
            <a href="/">DeepSeek 智能應用與跨境提效指南</a>
        </div>
        <p>聚焦 2026 最新 DeepSeek 網頁版登入入口、跨境流量分發與 AI 自動化部署</p>
    </header>

    <nav class="main-nav">
        <a href="/">首頁入口</a>
        <a href="/blog/">技術資訊大廳</a>
    </nav>

    <div class="wrapper">
        <main class="content-area">
            {# 承接子模板傳遞過來的真實核心內容 #}
            {{ content | safe }}
        </main>
        
        <aside class="sidebar">
            <h3>📂 最新技術指南推薦</h3>
            <ul class="sidebar-list">
                {# 強制全局側邊欄精準提取最新 5 篇文章，做好全站權重內鏈內循環 #}
                {% set sideCount = 0 %}
                {% for item in collections.posts %}
                    {% if sideCount < 5 %}
                        <li><a href="{{ item.url }}" title="{{ item.data.title }}">{{ item.data.title }}</a></li>
                        {% set sideCount = sideCount + 1 %}
                    {% endif %}
                {% else %}
                    <li style="color: #94a3b8;">暫無更新內容</li>
                {% endfor %}
            </ul>
        </aside>
    </div>

    <footer class="footer">
        {# 🎯 跨域名站群 SEO 戰略矩陣交叉內鏈鏈接鏈 (全繁體錨文本優化) #}
        <div class="friend-links">
            <strong>🌐 DeepSeek 跨境戰略矩陣聯盟：</strong>
            <a href="https://deepseek-chat.com" target="_blank">DeepSeek 智能對話大廳</a> |
            <a href="https://hk-deepseek.com" target="_blank">DeepSeek 香港繁體門戶</a> |
            <a href="https://deepseek-in.com" target="_blank">DeepSeek 國際跨境專區</a> |
            <a href="https://deepseek-1.com" target="_blank">DeepSeek 一號核心樞紐</a> |
            <a href="https://deepseek-my.com" target="_blank">DeepSeek 馬來西亞資訊網</a>
        </div>
        <p>&copy; 2026 deepseek-1.com. All Rights Reserved. 專注於搜索引擎優化與自動化提效矩陣。</p>
    </footer>

    {# 🎯 51.la 統計腳本完美配合位置：DOM 樹最末端 #}
    <script charset="UTF-8" id="LA_COLLECT" src="//sdk.51.la/js-sdk-pro.min.js"></script>
    <script>LA.init({id:"3K7l95Zodr0uFrIN",ck:"3K7l95Zodr0uFrIN"})</script>
</body>
</html>